Title: Changes the name of certain gifts of home delivered meals for seniors from "Meals on Wheels for Seniors" to "Home Delivered Meals for Seniors"
Summary: Changes the name of certain gifts of home delivered meals for seniors from "Meals on Wheels for Seniors" to "Home Delivered Meals for Seniors".
LawCode: Amd §§209-M & 626-a, Tax L (as proposed in S.5987 & A.4632)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to the senior wellness in nutrition fund
